TestGMP.cpp
Step 1. cd into the directory where TestGMP.cpp located.
Step 2. $g++ -lgmp -lntl TestGMP.cpp
        this will output a file a.out.
Step 3. $./a.out
        2^100 = 126765.........
        _
        _
        // input 2 numubers, such as 45 and 67
        3128
